---
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Omegon — Terminal-Native AI Agent Harness</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Single binary. Ten providers. Zero dependencies. A systems engineering harness for operators who ship." />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Tomorrow:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body>
  <nav class="topnav">
    <a href="/" class="topnav-logo">Ω Omegon</a>
    <div class="topnav-links">
      <a href="/docs/">Docs</a>
      <a href="/changelog">Changelog</a>
      <a href="https://github.com/styrene-lab/omegon">GitHub</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1 class="hero-title">Ω</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">Terminal-native AI agent harness</p>
      <p class="hero-tagline">
        Single binary. Ten providers. Zero dependencies.<br />
        For operators who ship.
      </p>

      <pre class="hero-install"><code>curl -fsSL https://omegon.styrene.dev/install.sh | sh</code></pre>

      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a href="/docs/quickstart" class="btn btn-primary">Quick Start →</a>
        <a href="/docs/" class="btn btn-secondary">Read the Docs</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="features">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">⚡</div>
        <h3>10 Inference Providers</h3>
        <p>Anthropic, OpenAI, Codex, OpenRouter, Groq, xAI, Mistral, Cerebras, HuggingFace, Ollama — native Rust clients with automatic failover and routing.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">🧠</div>
        <h3>Persistent Memory</h3>
        <p>Project knowledge survives across sessions. Semantic recall, episodic narratives, knowledge graphs. Not another markdown file — a real memory system.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">⑂</div>
        <h3>Parallel Execution</h3>
        <p>Cleave tasks into parallel git worktree children. Automatic merge, conflict detection, adversarial review. Ship in hours what takes days.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">🌳</div>
        <h3>Design Tree</h3>
        <p>263+ node knowledge graph tracking architecture decisions, dependencies, and implementation status. Not a task list — a design exploration system.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">📋</div>
        <h3>Spec-Driven Development</h3>
        <p>OpenSpec lifecycle: propose → spec → execute → verify → archive. Write specs before code. Given/When/Then scenarios as source of truth.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">🎮</div>
        <h3>Live TUI Dashboard</h3>
        <p>Terminal UI with instrument panels, context telemetry, segment rendering with model tags. Plus a web dashboard over WebSocket for remote monitoring.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="stats-bar">
      <div class="stat"><span class="stat-value">65,000+</span><span class="stat-label">lines of Rust</span></div>
      <div class="stat"><span class="stat-value">877</span><span class="stat-label">tests</span></div>
      <div class="stat"><span class="stat-value">15 MB</span><span class="stat-label">single binary</span></div>
      <div class="stat"><span class="stat-value">0</span><span class="stat-label">runtime dependencies</span></div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="docs-footer">
    <a href="https://github.com/styrene-lab/omegon">GitHub</a> ·
    <a href="https://github.com/styrene-lab/omegon/releases">Releases</a> ·
    <a href="https://github.com/styrene-lab/omegon/blob/main/LICENSE">BSL 1.1</a> ·
    © 2024–2026 Black Meridian, LLC
  </footer>
</body>
</html>

<style>
  .hero {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 60px 24px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: 80px;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    letter-spacing: -2px;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--fg);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .hero-tagline {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .hero-install {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 12px 24px;
    font-size: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .hero-install code {
    background: none;
    border: none;
    padding: 0;
    color: inherit;
  }

  .hero-cta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 10px 24px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.15s;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: var(--bg);
  }
  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: var(--accent-muted);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: var(--surface);
    color: var(--fg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .features {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .feature-card {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-dim);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 20px;
  }

  .feature-icon {
    font-size: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .feature-card h3 {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--fg);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .feature-card p {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .stats-bar {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 48px;
    padding: 24px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-dim);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-dim);
  }

  .stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .stat-value {
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--dim);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  .docs-footer {
    padding: 24px;
    text-align: center;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-dim);
    color: var(--dim);
    font-size: 12px;
  }
  .docs-footer a { color: var(--muted); }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-title { font-size: 48px; }
    .features { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .stats-bar { flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 24px; }
  }
</style>
